# Nano sketches (Timers Workshop)

Deliver **complete** `setup()` / `loop()` and `platformio.ini` when generating a project.

## Always

- `Wire.begin()` before I²C device `begin()` when using I²C.
- MPU6050 at **0x69** (`mpu.begin(0x69, &Wire, 0)`); DS3231 uses **0x68**.
- `Serial.begin(115200)` when helpful.
- Pins: NeoPixel **D6**, Servo **D9**, I²C **A4/A5** (see `02-hardware-pins.md`).

## Never

- PairLink, WiFi, WebSocket, `ESP32Servo`, or ESP32-only APIs.
- Libraries outside strict `lib_deps`.
- `analogRead` unless the user explicitly asks.

## VL53L0X / OLED

- Non-blocking `loop()`; limit OLED refresh rate if polling ToF quickly.
